r 2026 00:27:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/hibernator-superpowers-could-help-humans-treat-diabetes-and-alzheimers</guid></item><item><title>发作间期呼吸变异性与全身性惊厥发作后发作后低氧血症严重程度的关系</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/association-of-interictal-respiratory-variability-and-severity-of-postictal-hypoxemia-after-generalized-convulsive-seizures</link><description>在一项基于社区动脉粥样硬化风险神经认知研究 (ARIC-NCS) 的观察性队列研究中，脑叶和混合 CMB 的存在与痴呆发生相关。中风。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/association-of-interictal-respiratory-variability-and-severity-of-postictal-hypoxemia-after-generalized-convulsive-seizures2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Mar 2026 00:12:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/association-of-interictal-respiratory-variability-and-severity-of-postictal-hypoxemia-after-generalized-convulsive-seizures</guid></item><item><title>细胞内细菌调节口腔鳞状细胞癌的免疫微环境</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/intracellular-bacteria-modulate-the-immune-microenvironment-of-oral-squamous-cell-carcinoma</link><description>王等人。应用 INVADEseq 探测接受新辅助免疫治疗的口腔鳞状细胞癌患者的细胞内细菌。他们表明细菌调节免疫功效，识别特定的反应预测因子，并揭示细菌对预测因子和 cDC1 之间通信的影响。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/intracellular-bacteria-modulate-the-immune-microenvironment-of-oral-squamous-cell-carcinoma2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Mar 2026 23:57:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/intracellular-bacteria-modulate-the-immune-microenvironment-of-oral-squamous-cell-carcinoma</guid></item><item><title>血浆 p-tau217 临界值、肾功能、BMI 和贫血</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/plasma-p-tau217-cutoffs-kidney-function-bmi-and-anemia</link><description>与标准单一截止值相比，基于生物学的血浆 pTau217 阈值提高了 CKD 和贫血患者淀粉样蛋白 PET 阳性的诊断准确性，支持在阿尔茨海默病筛查中经济有效地实施生物标志物。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/plasma-p-tau217-cutoffs-kidney-function-bmi-and-anemia.png" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Mar 2026 23:42:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/plasma-p-tau217-cutoffs-kidney-function-bmi-and-anemia</guid></item><item><title>技术提前警报🙌</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/technical-advance-alert-%f0%9f%99%8c</link><description>https://doi.org/10.1172/jci.insight&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/technical-advance-alert-f09f998c2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Mar 2026 23:27:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/technical-advance-alert-%f0%9f%99%8c</guid></item><item><title>以 E3-ome 基因为中心的纲要揭示了人类 E3 连接酶的概况</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/the-e3-ome-gene-centric-compendium-reveals-the-human-e3-ligase-landscape</link><description>现已上线！ E3-ome 定义了人类泛素 E3 连接酶的全部库，创建了一个统一的资源来映射其在泛素和泛素样系统中的多样性。通过整合零散的知识，该框架为研究泛素信号传导和加速发现提供了基础。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/the-e3-ome-gene-centric-compendium-reveals-the-human-e3-ligase-landscape2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Mar 2026 23:12:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/the-e3-ome-gene-centric-compendium-reveals-the-human-e3-ligase-landscape</guid></item><item><title>绿松石鳉鱼免疫系统中与自发衰老相关的炎症和基因组不稳定性</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/spontaneous-aging-associated-inflammation-and-genome-instability-in-the-immune-system-of-turquoise-killifish</link><description>绿松石鳉鱼是天然的短命脊椎动物，可以作为衰老的模型系统。作者表明，鳉鱼的免疫系统表现出与年龄相关的转变，从而迅速出现炎症、基因组不稳定和功能衰退。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/spontaneous-aging-associated-inflammation-and-genome-instability-in-the-immune-system-of-turquoise-killifish.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Mar 2026 22:57:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/spontaneous-aging-associated-inflammation-and-genome-instability-in-the-immune-system-of-turquoise-killifish</guid></item></channel></rss>